---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceDetail from '../../../components/ServiceDetail.astro';
---
<Layout title="Implementation & Onboarding" description="A Salesforce implementation aligned with your strategy and embraced by your team. From analysis to go-live: Resolve IT guides you every step of the way.">
  <ServiceDetail
    lang="en"
    eyebrow="Service · Implementation & Onboarding"
    title="A Salesforce foundation your organisation can truly build on"
    intro="Salesforce is an incredibly powerful platform. But you only unlock its full potential when it is set up in line with your strategic goals, and embraced by your whole team. We make sure both happen."
    heroStats={[{ num: '300+', label: 'projects' }, { num: '24h', label: 'fast starts possible' }, { num: '5★', label: 'AppExchange' }]}
    image="/images/cases/case-1.jpg"
    whatTitle="From loose ambition to a working platform"
    whatText={[
      'Many implementations stall because technology takes the lead instead of your goals. We flip that around: we start with what you want to achieve and build the solution around it.',
      'Our consultants translate your processes into a clean, scalable Salesforce environment, delivered in short cycles, so you see value along the way and can adjust course. No big bang, just control.',
    ]}
    whatList={[
      'Configuration aligned with your strategic goals',
      'Clean data migration from your existing systems',
      'Adoption secured through training and guidance',
      'Built to scale, ready for the years ahead',
    ]}
    deliverables={[
      { icon: '🎯', title: 'Strategic design', text: 'A blueprint that translates your goals into concrete functionality and user stories.' },
      { icon: '🏗️', title: 'Working environment', text: 'A configured, tested Salesforce environment that fits your daily practice.' },
      { icon: '📦', title: 'Migrated data', text: 'Your existing data cleaned, validated and migrated to Salesforce.' },
      { icon: '🎓', title: 'Trained team', text: 'People who work confidently with the system from day one.' },
    ]}
    steps={[
      { title: 'Prepare', text: 'We analyse your needs, processes and goals and design the ideal solution, together with the people who will use it.' },
      { title: 'Design', text: 'We translate the vision into a concrete, actionable plan with detailed designs and user stories.' },
      { title: 'Build', text: 'We build along the roadmap, in close collaboration with your organisation and with short feedback loops.' },
      { title: 'Accelerate', text: 'We ensure a smooth transition with training and support, so your team is productive right away.' },
    ]}
    why={[
      { icon: '🤝', title: 'One team with you', text: 'We work side by side with your people. Short lines, fast decisions, no surprises.' },
      { icon: '🧭', title: 'Strategy first', text: 'We don’t build features for the sake of it, but solutions that serve your goals.' },
      { icon: '🌱', title: 'Beyond go-live', text: 'We stay involved with support and further development. Your success is our success.' },
    ]}
    faqs={[
      { q: 'How long does an implementation take?', a: 'It depends on scope and complexity. Simple projects can go live very quickly; larger implementations run in short cycles so you see results along the way. In a first conversation we give you a realistic estimate.' },
      { q: 'Do you migrate our existing data?', a: 'Yes. We clean, validate and migrate your data to Salesforce in a structured way.' },
      { q: 'How do you ensure our team uses the system?', a: 'Adoption is as important as the technology. We involve users early, train on concrete tasks and guide the rollout.' },
      { q: 'What do you need from us?', a: 'Mainly involvement: access to the right people and clarity on your goals. We take care of the rest. <a href="/en/contact">Get in touch</a> to get acquainted.' },
    ]}
  />
</Layout>
